nk ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-vat-the-innosmart-dc-i7wg\/#tong_quan_san_pham\" >T\u1ed5ng quan s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-vat-the-innosmart-dc-i7wg\/#tinh_nang_san_pham\" >T\u00ednh n\u0103ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-vat-the-innosmart-dc-i7wg\/#thong_so_ky_thuat\" >Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong_quan_san_pham\"><\/span>T\u1ed5ng quan s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e1y thu v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 INNOSMART DC-i7WG l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i camera 8 MP v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng zoom quang h\u1ecdc 12X v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 ghi h\u00ecnh linh ho\u1ea1t, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tinh_nang_san_pham\"><\/span>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e1y thu v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 INNOSMART DC-i7WG s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, camera v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i 8 MP v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\/2.7\u201c CMOS cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c. V\u1edbi zoom quang h\u1ecdc 12X, c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc 10X v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 12X, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00f3ng to c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u.<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e1y c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khung h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u0111a 30fps, gi\u00fap h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu. K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f9ng qu\u00e9t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn A3 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea5y n\u00e9t t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nh\u01b0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eafng, t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0u, l\u1ea5y n\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh theo nhu c\u1ea7u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u00e1y c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ghi h\u00ecnh video v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m, gi\u00fap d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u01b0u l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng, xoay, t\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00f3ng b\u0103ng, \u0111en tr\u1eafng, \u00e2m b\u1ea3n, PIP, ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u, mask v\u00e0 mosaic, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb. M\u00e1y c\u00f2n t\u00edch h\u1ee3p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LCD, cho ph\u00e9p xem tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 VGA, HDMI.<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e1y c\u0169ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n t\u1eeb xa, kh\u00f3a Kensington, v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng LED h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thong_so_ky_thuat\"><\/span>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 42.027%;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt<\/th>\n<th style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">Chi ti\u1ebft<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i camera<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">8 MP<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">Zoom<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">Quang h\u1ecdc 12X, C\u01a1 h\u1ecdc 10X, K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 12X<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">C\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">1\/2.7\u201c CMOS<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">\u1ed0ng k\u00ednh<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">ff=4.7~47mm, FF=1.6~3.0<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khung h\u00ecnh<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">30fps (max)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f9ng qu\u00e9t<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">A3<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">L\u1ea5y n\u00e9t<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng\/ th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">T\u00edn hi\u1ec7u xu\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">1080P<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i (chi\u1ec1u ngang)<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">\u2265 1000 TV lines<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eafng<\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 56.8919%;\">T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng\/ th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 42.027%;\">T\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh \u